  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510250/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765196155\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510250/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765196155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/510250/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765196155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>If you love pixelated retro games, this is for you and get ready for some intense retro space shooting! <br>Fight again waves of invaders in this arcade space shooter and collect power-ups to increase your fire power. Try to beat your high-score in Classic, Time Attack or Hardcore mode or challenge your friend in Multiplayer mode. If you like classic arcade shooters then you will love Super Destronaut.",
